flowRoot.flowPara: Private companies run different portions of Tokyo's rail network.
Many rail companies also own large department stores throughout Tokyo.
Tokyo's rail system is not managed by a single entity.
The number of customers in the queue increases as Department Stores are built to accelerate the game.
Give 1 customer to store owner if it matches
Ignore stores that don't match customers
Department stores match all customer types
When you move through others' track, they gain income (cards).
Each card is a region of Tokyo
Build store in location to make
